      |\n|    |               | modu |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | ated |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | arti |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | icia |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               |      |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | inte |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | lige |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | ce   |        |         |             |             |\n+----+---------------+------+--------+---------+-------------+-------------+\n| 7  | Yotz          | Exte | Chris  | 319624. | 2017-01-06  | ClosedLost  |\n|    |               | ded  |        | 0       |             |             |\n|    |               | seco |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | dary |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | infr |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | stru |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | ture |        |         |             |             |\n+----+---------------+------+--------+---------+-------------+-------------+\n| 8  | Oloo          | Conf | Chris  | 321016. | 2017-03-08  | ClosedLost  |\n|    |               | gura |        | 6       |             |             |\n|    |               | le   |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | web- |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | nabl |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | d    |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | data |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | ware |        |         |             |             |\n|    |               | ouse |        |   